| Proyecto       | Puede referenciar            |
| -------------- | ---------------------------- |
| Domain         | NADA                         |
| Application    | Domain                       |
| Infrastructure | Application + Domain         |
| Api            | Application + Infrastructure |

src/
 ├── Api/                 ← HTTP REST
 │    └── Program.cs
 ├── Worker/              ← Background jobs
 │    └── Program.cs
 ├── Grpc/                ← gRPC
 │    └── Program.cs
 ├── Application/
 ├── Domain/
 └── Infrastructure/

✔ Application tiene su propio DI
✔ Infrastructure tiene su propio DI
✔ API solo ensambla
Controller
   ↓
Application (Use Case)
   ↓
Interface (IMemberRepository)
   ↓
Infrastructure (Mongo)


